00:08.532 --> 00:10.602
He is walking his dog.

00:11.195 --> 00:12.696
The dog is his.

00:14.336 --> 00:15.729
That is her wine.

00:16.373 --> 00:18.307
The wine is hers.

00:20.028 --> 00:21.529
This is my toy.

00:22.353 --> 00:23.882
It's mine, mine, mine!

00:25.853 --> 00:27.219
This is our room.

00:27.806 --> 00:29.644
The room is ours.

00:31.069 --> 00:32.278
Is that your food?

00:33.142 --> 00:35.129
Yours looks better than mine.

00:36.474 --> 00:37.911
That is their horse.

00:39.493 --> 00:41.487
The horse is theirs.

